data.description: Fantastic golf course lot ready for next owner  right on the 7th hole, come and enjoy breakfast or an evening cocktail with this breathtaking setting! Both the front and back of the home have a screened in porch so you get to choose to enjoy the beautiful Florida weather in the back or front of the home. Upon entering the home, you will see the main area is laminated, beautifully done kitchen cabinets with a matching granite, stainless-steel appliances and recess lighting. Master bedroom is very spacious and just wait until you see the closet- it's almost another room! Guest bedroom/office is adjoining the 2nd bathroom, split floor plan to give the additional privacy and personal space. Home has accordion shutters, a metal roof, gutters and so many extras. The furniture is negotiable. and sellers can work with you on negotiating a closing date that will work for you. Outside of the home being an amazing one, the community itself is one of a kind, some of the most welcoming, kind and fun people that you have yet to meet! Come Join Spanish Lakes and see why everyone loves to be here, included in your monthly fee, you have a private golf course (free to play) 2 Swimming pools, gym, tennis, shuffleboard, pickleball, Bocce, aerobics, pool tables, arts/crafts, grass cutting, trash pick up. There is so much to do here, a great home at an affordable price! Home is also equipped with a whole house generator that is brand spanking new!
